summary: An Ordinance transferring the sum of Eighty-three and 05/100 (83.05) Dollars, from Local Improvement District No. 1579 Fund, into the General Fund of the City of Seattle. for the purpose of reimbursing said General Fund, for the deficiency in the Fixed Estimate of said district, for the improvement of Thirty-sixth Avenue North et al., by Grading, as provided for in Ordinance No. 16854, creating Local Improvement District No. 1579.
